{
  "id": "63c1911469a188001d7eab50",
  "title": "音律の比較",
  "created": 1673629973,
  "updated": 1673881750,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c1911469a188001d7eab50",
      "text": "音律の比較",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb20",
      "text": "音律の比較",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629978
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb22",
      "text": "\t[ピタゴラス音律] 1, 9/8, 81/64, 4/3, 3/2, 27/16, 243/128, 2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e3a2aff09e0000029368",
      "text": "\t\t> 音階の全ての音と音程を周波数比3:2の純正な[完全五度]に基づいて導出する音律 [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ピタゴラス音律 ピタゴラス音律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782179,
      "updated": 1673782214
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e3a5aff09e0000029369",
      "text": "\t\t1:2は「オクターブ違い、同じ音名」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782182,
      "updated": 1673782184
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb24",
      "text": "\t\tある適当な音Dから上下に3:2を3回やることで7音からなる音階ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb25",
      "text": "\t\t　これは現代の平均律の白鍵から半音の6%程度のズレに収まっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673631106
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56749774b1700000c9bbc",
      "text": "\t\t [周波数3/2倍は7半音と2cents]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881418,
      "updated": 1673881557
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb26",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/e77e2c0792fae93b1231feae47372f95]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1957eaff09e0000b5a645",
      "text": "　　これをもっと繰り返していくと、全音階よりも「少し高い音」「少し低い音」ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631103,
      "updated": 1673631146
    },
    {
      "id": "63c195a9aff09e0000b5a647",
      "text": "　　　それがシャープとフラットになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631146,
      "updated": 1673631153
    },
    {
      "id": "63c195b0aff09e0000b5a648",
      "text": "　　　この時点ではドのシャープとレのフラットは違う音だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631153,
      "updated": 1673632742
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e37caff09e0000029365",
      "text": "　　　[https://gyazo.com/7d0f483d34c2d19a09201958c90205fa]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782141,
      "updated": 1673782142
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e37daff09e0000029366",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ピタゴラスコンマ ピタゴラスコンマ - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782142,
      "updated": 1673782156
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e38baff09e0000029367",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tG# - Ab = `log(3, 2) * 12 % 1` = 0.01955000865387646",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782156,
      "updated": 1673807096
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e5fcaff09e0000db62f8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t　これが0になるならオクターブ違いの同じ音とみなせるのたが、実際にはズレがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782780,
      "updated": 1673782811
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1957faff09e0000b5a646",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t`_ * 12` = 0.23460010384651753",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631103,
      "updated": 1673782771
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e61faff09e0000db62f9",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t　このズレは1/4半音程度だとわかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782816,
      "updated": 1673782835
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb27",
      "text": "\t[純正律] 1, 9/8, 5/4, 4/3, 3/2, 5/3, 15/8, 2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629991
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb28",
      "text": "　　>Cを基準とした場合、Cの3度上がE、5度上がG、次にGの3度上がB、5度上がD、さらにCの5度下がF、Fの3度上がAとなり、これらを1 オクターヴ内に配列することでハ長調の全音階が得られる。 [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/純正律 純正律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb29",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/5820277b801d1dfd83bf42fbbc5d72c9]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2a",
      "text": "\t　幹音から5/4倍することでシャープの半音が、4/5倍することでフラットの半音が得られる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673631405
    },
    {
      "id": "63c196aeaff09e0000b5a64a",
      "text": "\t　　[https://gyazo.com/b0c842b797808a84e4b078de35495d13]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631407,
      "updated": 1673631805
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1983caff09e0000b5a64b",
      "text": "　　　ラのシャープとソのフラットは存在しないって理解でいいのかな？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631805,
      "updated": 1673631849
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3bfedaff09e0000dcc714",
      "text": "　　　　今でもそういう書き方はあまりしないのは、これが理由なのかな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673773038,
      "updated": 1673773053
    },
    {
      "id": "63c4449caff09e0000f2f06e",
      "text": "　　　　\tA#ではなくBb, GbではなくF#って書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673807004,
      "updated": 1673807022
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19869aff09e0000b5a64c",
      "text": "　　  ドのシャープとレのフラットはもちろん違う音",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631849,
      "updated": 1673632735
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1964caff09e0000b5a649",
      "text": "\t平均律 [$ (\\sqrt[12]{2})^n ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631309,
      "updated": 1673631309
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e40baff09e000002936a",
      "text": "\t\t>十二平均律とは、1オクターヴを12等分した音律である。隣り合う音（半音）の周波数比は等しく[$ (\\sqrt[12]{2})^n : 1 ] となる。[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/平均律 平均律 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782283,
      "updated": 1673782494
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2b",
      "text": "\t　「1オクターブは12半音である」と考えて、半音の周波数比率を平均化して同じ比率にした",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673782502
    },
    {
      "id": "63c198c8aff09e0000b5a64d",
      "text": "\t\tドのシャープとレのフラットが同じ音になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631944,
      "updated": 1673760329
    },
    {
      "id": "63c38e48aff09e0000157729",
      "text": "\t\t「Q: なんで同じ音に2通りの表記があるの？ A:昔は違ったんだよ」 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673760329,
      "updated": 1673760370
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3937e6eb406000099d17a",
      "text": " \t\t今でも意味が違うケースもあると聞いたことがある[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673761663,
      "updated": 1673782462
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3938d6eb406000099d17b",
      "text": " \t\t\tしっかり理解できていないので説明できないけど",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673761678,
      "updated": 1673782462
    },
    {
      "id": "63c393a06eb406000099d17c",
      "text": " \t\t\t純正律の文脈というわけではなかったはず・・なんだっけな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673761698,
      "updated": 1673782462
    },
    {
      "id": "63c198c8aff09e0000b5a64e",
      "text": "\t\t>[フレット式楽器]やモノコードなどでは、幾何的に弦の分割点を設定することで平均律を実現できる。また、フレット式楽器では、平均律以外の半音の音程が一定でない音律では、各弦に対するフレット間隔が揃わず、直線のフレットを用いるには不都合である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673631944,
      "updated": 1673782469
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e4c8aff09e000002936b",
      "text": "\t\t\tなるほど[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782473,
      "updated": 1673782480
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3e4d2aff09e000002936c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673782482,
      "updated": 1673782483
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2c",
      "text": "\ttable::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2d",
      "text": "\t \t平均律\t純正律\t\tピタ\t",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2e",
      "text": "\t D\t0\t0\t1/1\t0\t1/1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb2f",
      "text": "\t Eb\t100\t\t\t90\t256/243",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb30",
      "text": "\t E\t200\t204\t9/8\t204\t9/8",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb31",
      "text": "\t  F\t300\t\t\t294\t32/27",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb32",
      "text": "\t F#\t400\t386\t5/4\t408\t81/64",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb33",
      "text": "\t G\t500\t498\t4/3\t498\t4/3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb34",
      "text": "\t G#\t600\t\t\t612\t729/512",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb35",
      "text": "\t A\t700\t702\t3/2\t702\t3/2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb36",
      "text": "\t Bb\t800\t\t\t792\t128/81",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb37",
      "text": "\t B\t900\t884\t5/3\t906\t27/16",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb38",
      "text": "\t C\t1000\t\t\t996\t16/9",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb39",
      "text": "\t C#\t1100\t1088\t15/8\t1110\t243/128",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3b",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3c",
      "text": "\t純正律(間違い)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3d",
      "text": "\t\tある適当な音Dから上下に3:2と5:4を2回やることで11音からなる音階ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3e",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/bb609bd946380d81a95f98de32d215bd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb3f",
      "text": "\t　あれ、この図はBとかがないな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb40",
      "text": "\t　　それはピタゴラス音律同様に3:2を3回やったものか？？？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb41",
      "text": "\t　　なんだか怪しいので後で確認する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c19114aff09e0000caeb42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629973,
      "updated": 1673629973
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1911caff09e0000caeb43",
      "text": "from [音律の歴史]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673629981,
      "updated": 1673629981
    }
  ]
}